1. *Tajno* sam se nadala da će mi dati posao. (I secretly hoped that they would give me the job.)
2. Nadam se da ovo ostane *tajna*. (I hope that this remains a secret.)
3. Želim ti reći nešto *tajno*. (I want to tell you something in secret.)
4. *Tajni* sastanak će se održati sutra uveče. (A secret meeting will be held tomorrow evening.)
5. Oni su *tajno* planirali svoje venčanje. (They secretly planned their wedding.)
6. Želim da imam *tajnost* u mom životu. (I want to have privacy in my life.)
7. Vlada je odlučila da zadrži ovu informaciju u *tajnosti*. (The government decided to keep this information in secrecy.)
8. Policija je pronašla *tajnu* sobu u kući osumnjičenog. (The police found a secret room in the suspect's house.)
9. *Tajni* dokumenti su procurili u javnost. (Secret documents have leaked to the public.)
10. On je *tajanstven* muškarac. (He is a mysterious man.)

Note: The word "tajno" in Serbian means "secretly" or "secret", while its other forms such as "tajna", "tajni" and "tajnost" have different meanings but still related to the concept of secrecy.